{"tid":1856571,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"急：大埔中心一田 出現 超級帶菌者","createTime":"2020-02-01T16:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T18:29:56.000Z","uid":322909,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b0da0a61172132a858fa55ac63d71c249f0f01e0","tid":1856571,"uid":322909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:44:57.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1191070\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1191070&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=36fdf910\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1191070&h=068bc7c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1191070</a><br />\n<br />\n伊利沙伯醫院同事確認，這名兒童去過大埔中心食肆晚飯，之後在一田超級市場暈倒<br />\n當其時有嘔吐物流出及咳嗽，有一班穿着黑衫年青人上前協助，扶起小朋友，醫務衛生署呼籲這班青年請立即到大埔那打素接受觀察，伊利沙伯主診醫生確認這名小朋友超級肺炎帶菌者。<br />\n<br />\n[星島日報] 【武漢肺炎】伊院接收懷疑染病小童 女親友陪同<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1191070\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1191070&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=36fdf910\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1191070&h=068bc7c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1191070</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n☝🏻☝🏻☝🏻即刻轉畀其他人，希望嗰班年青人睇到！"},{"pid":"9d4cbe2c45e46bc1d0cfeb1a6cc242693131905b","tid":1856571,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:45:25.000Z","msg":"係咪支那蛆"},{"pid":"89ebed1e34d554e7ab510d87cafa9570af67919e","tid":1856571,"uid":6061,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T16:45:31.000Z","msg":"屌你 未話撚左係假"},{"pid":"f398a8f91ca0d3d337289ce9c9d1de387efccde6","tid":1856571,"uid":49018,"lik